<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Home</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Barlow', sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            min-height: 100vh;
            flex-direction: column;
        }

 
        header {
            background-color: #03ca81;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        main {
            flex-grow: 1;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: black;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-top: auto;
        }

        a {
            color: green;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .postAdder {
            background-color: #16db93;;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .post-container {
            padding-top: 50px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            justify-items: center;
        }

        .post {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .post h2 {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .post p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }
        .postAdder:hover {
            background-color: darkgreen;
        }

        .text-gradient {
            /* Add gradient effect if needed */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container" style="flex: 1;display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <header>
            <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>
        </header>
        <main>
            <p>Thank you for using our application. We're glad to have you on board!</p>
            <p>Explore the features and let us know if you need any assistance.</p>
            <a href="/"></a>
            <a href="/logout" class="border-shadow postAdder">
                <span class="text-gradient">Log Out<i class="fas fa-user"></i></span>
            </a>
            <a href="/tasks">See Tasks</a>
            <div class="post-container">
                <% posts.forEach(post => { %>
                    <div class="post">
                        <h2><%= post.title %></h2>
                        <p><%= post.content %></p>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>Â© 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
